Module: Stop Forum Spam

This module uses stopforumspam.com to check newly registered users
against their database of known spammers

Installation instructions:
--------------------------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "stopforumspam" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Stop Forum Spam" and configure its settings.

